      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "All the scripts used for this data treatment are available for examination and reuse on the ENPKG GitHub organization, with an overview of the workflow and the links to the different repositories available at https://github.com/enpkg/enpkg_workflow.",
