    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/molecular-networking-construction/009",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The features from all considered samples are then classically aligned based on their RT and m/z to obtain a feature quantification table of dimensions N \u00d7 M (N represents the number of samples and M the number of features) and their associated fragmentation spectra.",
      "asbval:note": "Feature tables with cluster/network assignments are generated as part of the workflow.",
