      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Molecular networking was performed in Python using the matchms (v0.20.0) package... Spectral matching was performed in Python using the matchms (v0.20.0) package against an in silico database (ISDB-LOTUS)... Matching candidates were reranked according to the taxonomic distance... The scripts used for spectral matching and taxonomical/chemical reweighting are available at https://github.com/enpkg/enpkg_full/tree/main/03_enpkg_mn_isdb_isdb_taxo",
      "asbval:note": "enpkg_mn_isdb_taxo explicitly confirmed for molecular networking and taxonomically-informed annotation.",
