      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "we developed the MEMO approach... we push this concept further and propose shifting from a data set-centric to a sample-centric approach... The Experimental Natural Products Knowledge Graph (ENPKG) framework",
      "asbval:note": "ENPKG is the overarching framework described in the paper; the tool entry includes metadata fields (canonical_url, install, version_used, etc.) that are not directly addressed in the paper but are consistent with the framework's GitHub repositories.",
