      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The chemical structures can also be enriched with their reported bioactivity against a selected biological target in ChEMBL... To allow for faster identification of compounds with an already reported activity against a given target, we implemented an automatic fetching and formatting of ChEMBL compounds with an activity reported against a given target.",
      "asbval:note": "Confirmed. ChEMBL integration is optional and used for bioactivity enrichment.",
